snippet.textDisplay: Superb Composition, Credit goes to Amit Trivedi for bringing up such fresh Music. A Rajasthani folk song is Tremendously blend with main stream instruments.. and Mame Khan ji tussi toh cha gaye.. The Jugalbandi @ 4.10 minutes performed between Khartaal player and Drumist is Masterpiece. And, d must listen part  when tempo of d song goes high... it drove me crazy.. cannot stop myself listening this masterpiece again and again.. will surely expect more and more such creation in future, Amit Ji..
